          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "When Nox dies, their body combusts in a flash of white-hot flame that deals 5d6 fire damage to creatures in a 20-foot burst (DC 21 basic Reflex save). Nox's gear and treasure are unaffected by the flames and are left in a pile where they died.",
